Dayda

City of New York

This is a catalog of datasets organized and made more accessible from the City of New York, providing simple dowloadable CSV and JSON files, as well as Postman Collections you can use as part of workflows and other automation.

    2006 - 2012 English Language Arts (ELA) Test Results - Borough - Gender

    Latest available data and trends in the state assessment results of English Language Arts for grades 3 through 8. Data are disaggregated by borough and gender.

    2006 - 2012 English Language Arts (ELA) Test Results - Borough - Ethnicity

    Latest available data and trends in the state assessment results of English Language Arts for grades 3 through 8. Data are disaggregated by borough and student ethnicity.

    2006 - 2012 English Language Arts (ELA) Test Results - Borough - ELL

    Latest available data and trends in the state assessment results of English Language Arts for grades 3 through 8. Data are disaggregated by borough and ELL status.

    2006 - 2012 English Language Arts (ELA) Test Results - Borough - All Students

    Latest available data and trends in the state assessment results of English Language Arts for grades 3 through 8. Data are disaggregated by borough.

    2006 - 2012 English Language Arts (ELA) Test Results - Citywide - All Students

    Latest available data and trends in the state assessment results of English Language Arts for grades 3 through 8.
